# Keep the build context tiny — everything below is fetched inside the
# Dockerfile (ComfyUI, models) or doesn't belong in the image (git history,
# CI config, docs). Without this, the build sends the whole worktree to
# the Docker daemon on every build invocation.
.git/
.github/
.gitignore
README.md
WORKER_VERSION
*.md
__pycache__/
*.pyc
